extensionDescription.message: Facebook Container wašu aktiwitu Facebook wot zbytka wašeje webaktiwity izoluje, zo by Facebook při tym haćił, wam zwonka websydła Facebook přez placki třećich slědować.
extensionDescription.description: Description of the extension. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

in-fbc-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened into Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

in-fbc-p1.message: Facebook móže wam nětko na tutym sydle slědować. Zo byšće tute sydło z Facebook Container wotstronił, wubjerće „Sydła, kotrež su dowolene w Facebook Container“, zo byšće jo z lisćiny wotstronił.

on-facebook-subhead.message: Na Facebook a sydłach w škitanym wobłuku Facebook Container
on-facebook-subhead.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened into Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

on-facebook-p1.message: Tutón symbol so w adresowym polu Firefox jewi, hdyž sydła wopytujeće, kotrež Facebook słušeja, abo sydła, kotrež sće Facebook Container přidał.
on-facebook-p1.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened into Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

on-facebook-p2.message: Tute sydła trjebaja přistup na wašu identitu Facebook (abo dyrbja wědźeć, štó sće), zo bychu fungowali. To tež rěka, zo Facebook móže wšemu slědować, štož na tutych sydłach činiće.
on-facebook-p2.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop up when the user is on Facebook.

notOnFacebookHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

notOnFacebookText.message: Tute sydło je zwonka Facebook Container. To Facebbook poćežuje, wam po webje slědować.
notOnFacebookText.description: This is shown in the body of the panel pop-up when the user is NOT on a Facebook website, which has been automatically opened OUTSIDE Facebook Container. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

onUnknownSiteHeader.message: Tute sydło w Facebook Container njeje.
onUnknownSiteHeader.description: This is shown at the top of the panel pop-up when the user is on an "unknown" website - e.g., about:newtab. DO NOT TRANSLATE "Facebook Container".

facebookContainer.description: This is the name of the extension, and appears at the top of all onboarding panels. Please do not translate "Facebook Container".

onboarding1-subhead.description: This is the subhead of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding1-p1.message: Facebook móže wjace hač Facebook.com slědować. Tłóčatce „Spodoba so“ a „Dźělić“ na přikład móžetej wam wšudźe slědować, hdźež sće był - samo na stronach, na kotrychž njejsće ženje na „Spodoba so“ abo „Dźělić“ kliknył.
onboarding1-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of onboarding panel 1. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding1-p2.message: Facebook Container škitany wobłuk mjez sydłami a zbytkom interneta wutworja, zo by je ćešo za Facebook, wam online slědować.

onboarding2-subhead.message: Na Facebook a sydłach w škitanym wobłuku Facebook Container
onboarding2-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding2-alt.description: This is alternative text for the icon in the second onboarding panel

onboarding2-p1.message: Tutón symbol so w adresowym polu Firefox jewi, hdyž sydła kaž Facebook.com wopytujeće, kotrež su w škitanym wobłuku Facebook Container.
onboarding2-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the second onboarding panel.

onboarding2-p2.message: Tute sydła trjebaja přistup na wašu identitu Facebook (abo dyrbja wědźeć, štó sće), zo bychu fungowali. To tež rěka, zo Facebook móže wšemu slědować, štož na tutych sydłach činiće.
onboarding2-p2.description: This is the second paragraph of the second onboarding panel. Please do not translate "Facebook Container"

onboarding4-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-p1.message: Samo hdyž na Facebook njejsće, móže wam Facebook online slědować. Tłóčatka, kotrež wam zmóžnjeja, něšto na Facebook słać abo so z wašim kontom Facebook pola websydłow přizjewić, přesćěhowaki wobsahuja. Facebook Container budźe tute přesćěhowaki blokować a płótny symbol zwobraznić, zo by wam pokazał, hdźež su so přesćěhowaki wotstronili.
onboarding4-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding4-img.message: Tutón wobraz demonstruje, kak so płoćikowy symbol Facebook Container na stronje pódla tłóčatka „Spodoba so“ Facebook.
onboarding4-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the fourth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-subhead.message: Z Facebook na druhich sydłach přizjewić
onboarding5-subhead.description: This is the subhead for the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-p1.message: Zo byšće swoje přizjewjenje na druhich sydłach wužiwał, dyrbiće je do škitaneho wobłuka přesunyć. Klikńće na płótny symbol a wubjerće deleka ‚Sydło we Facebook Container‘.
onboarding5-p1.description: This is the first paragraph of the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-img.message: Tutón wobraz demonstruje, kak so tłóčatko za přidawanje sydła do Facebook Container we woknje pokazuje.
onboarding5-img.description: This is alternative text for the image shown in the fifth onboarding panel.

onboarding5-p2.message: To wam zmóžnja, so pola Facebook přizjewić, ale Facebook móže wašej aktiwiće na tym sydle slědować.
onboarding5-p2.description: This is the second paragraph on the fifth onboarding panel.

btn-allow.description: This is a button to allows users to whitelist the domain, adding it to the Facebook container.

btn-cancel.description: This is a button to cancel out of the onboarding panel.

btn-next.description: This is a button to continue to the next onboarding panel.

btn-back.description: This is a button that returns the user to the previous onboarding panel.

btn-done.description: This is a button the user clicks to close out the panel when they have finished reading the text.

btn-arrow-back.description: This is alternative text for the back arrow button.

btn-arrow-forward.description: This is alternative text for the arrow icon next to the "How Facebook Container Works" link

no-trackers-p1.message: Facebook Container njeje žane přesćěhowaki Facebook na tutej stronje namakał. Ale strona móže hišće druhe typy přesćěhowakow wobsahować.

learn-more.description: This is a link that opens a page with more information about Facebook Container.

how-fbc-works.description: This is a button that opens the Facebook Container onboarding flow.

trackers-detected-subhead.description: This is a subhead, and it means that the add on has protected the user by blocking Facebook trackers.

trackers-detected-p1.message: Tłóčatka Facebook, kotrež so na nakupowanskich, powěsćowych a druhich sydłach jewja, přesćěhowaki wobsahuja, kotrež Facebook zdźěleja, hdźež sće we webje był. Samo hdyž tute tłóčatka ženje njewužiwaće, zo byšće ze „Spodoba so“ markěrował abo dźělił, móža přesćěhowaki hišće daty wo wašim přehladowanju zběrać. Facebook Container tute přesćěhowaki blokuje.

trackers-detected-p2.message: Facebook Container tute přesćěhowaki blokuje. Jeli wšak na tute tłóčatka kliknjeće, móže wam Facebook slědować.

trackers-detected-fence-alt.message: Płoćikowy symbol Facebook Container ze škitom.
trackers-detected-fence-alt.description: This is alternative text describing the container fence icon.

sites-added-subhead.message: Sydła, kotrež su dowolene w Facebook Container

sites-included.description: This is a header for the list of websites that are in the Facebook Container by default. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the language.

no-sites-added.description: This message is shown beneath the 'SITES YOU’VE ALLOWED' list header when no sites have been added to the contaner.

sites-allowed.description: This is the header for the list of sites the user has manually added into the Facebook Container. Capitalized letters are preferred if that makes sense/is feasible for the lanaguage.

sites-added-p1.message: Facebook Container sydła Facebbok do škitaneho wobłuka zamka. Móžeće dalše websydła do škitaneho wobłuka zapřijeć, ale to Facebook zmóžnja, wjace wašeho webpřehladowanja slědować.

button-allow-site.description: Button text that allows sites to be added to the Facebook Container

button-remove-site.description: Button text that removes an already-added site from the Facebook Container to the default container

button-remove-site-tooltip.message: Dokelž to je sydło, kotrež Facebook słuša, njeda so z Facebook Container wotstronić.
button-remove-site-tooltip.description: Tooltip that is displayed when hovering over the remove site button

remove-site-p1.message: Hdyž tute sydło z Facebook Container wotstronjeće, to rěka, zo funkcija „Z Facebook přizjewić“ hižo njefunguje a so slědowace placki Facebook zhašeja.

remove-site-p2.message: Jeli chceće so zaso pola Facebook přizjewić, dyrbiće jón zaso Facebook Container přidać.

add-site-subhead.message: Slědowanje přez Facebook na tutym sydle dowolić?

add-site-p1.message: To wam zmóžnja, so pola Facebook přizjewić, dowoluje wšak Facebook slědować, štož na tutym sydle činiće.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-share.message: Facebook Container je tute tłóčatko znjemóžnił a Facebook při tym haćił, wašemu wopytej na tutej stronje slědować.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-login.message: Facebook Container je přesćěhowaki Facebook zablokował. Jeli „Z Facebook na tutym sydle přizjewić“ wužiwaće, móže wam Facebook slědować.

inPageUI-tooltip-prompt-p2.message: Jeli chceće funkciju „Z Facebook přizjewić“ wužiwać, móže Facebook wašej aktiwiće na tutym sydle slědować. To móže jemu pomhać, so z wašim žiwjenjom online lěpje zeznać.

inPageUI-tooltip-button-share-passive.message: Jeli na tute tłóčatko kliknjeće, móže Facebook wašemu wopytej na tutym sydle slědować.
